From c43bf5ab777f742a269d481703572214b4a657a9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 19:04:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add Psychology Layer V2: conversation streaks, achievements,
 at-risk reminders

- supabase/psychology_layer_v2.sql: conversation_streaks table (per match),
  AFTER INSERT trigger on messages that extends a streak when both
  participants send a genuine (allow-listed, non-system) message on the same
  UTC day, advisory-locked and dedupe-safe; awards global per-user
  achievements (reuses user_achievements) and fires deduped milestone
  notifications at 3/7/14/30 days; RLS (participants read own, admins read
  all); additive notification types conversation_streak_milestone and
  conversation_streak_at_risk
- lib/conversation-streaks.ts: streak read + derive helpers (active days,
  at-risk), UTC-based
- Database types: conversation_streaks table + ConversationStreakRow
- Messages page: momentum summary card + per-row streak badge; on-visit
  at-risk reminders (deduped per match), mirroring your_turn_reminder
- Chat header: streak pill next to momentum status
- Notification priority + wallet achievement labels for new keys
- Admin: active / 7-day conversation streak stat cards

Excludes system message types (story_*, gift_reaction, private_media_opened/
expired, call_event) from streak activity. Push kept out of scope. Does not
touch private media viewer/API, gifts economy, wallet payments, Paystack,
Gold purchase, or the daily reward claim function.
